<Layout
  title="How to Build a Mobile App For Your Shogun Website"
  description="Open up to learn the best way to create a mobile app for your Shogun website, risk-free, with the easiest path to a positive ROI."
>
  <Nav />

  <section class="py-20 md:py-32 px-4">
